Package ariba.ui.meta.layouts Description

Set of meta-data aware UI components for UI generation.

All AW/Widgets components can be incorporated in MetaUI generated interfaces, usually without any wrapping by using the m:IncludeComponent tag. However, some require some meta-data-aware wrapper components, and those are provided here.

See Also:
ariba.ui.meta.annotations, ariba.ui.meta.core, ariba.ui.meta.persistence
